{"tid":1543242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跳閘係冇成本抗爭，捉到都唔使交錢","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:03:23.000Z","uid":190579,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69c702d03ae91afd8e36fa8963aefa3710d0b0fb","tid":1543242,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"重開post<br />\n<br />\ntldr:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1) 話冇錢喺身，留地址，之後唔交，吹你唔脹<br />\n<br />\n2) 唔好講粗口</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">前黨鐵查飛狗：教你認識查飛狗，跳閘救港 所慳嘅錢可以捐出去！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531661</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>代前黨鐵查飛狗老友出post!<br />\n教人跳就好多post喇，依家就教點認查飛狗同萬一被截查後果。<br />\n<br />\n『本人做過2年黨鐵查飛狗，見到有好多手足坐黨鐵仲好驚唔敢跳，唔知比人捉到會點，所以寫呢個攻略同大家講，其實係跳閘係最大後果係比<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">$500/無後果/危險性極低/佢吹你吾</span></span>脹』<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n『便衣查飛衣著打扮』<br />\n入付費區前望清楚有無查飛狗！有時會係閘前附近伏人，好似好危險，但其實好撚易認，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">通常2人一組，著有領嘅衫，卡其褲，（唔比著背心，裙，牛仔褲，無領T</span></span>），一個站最多都係2組。整個查飛組應該有6-9隊，每隊5-6人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n『跳閘後不幸被便衣查飛狗截停，第一樣就係跑！！！』<br />\n（被人截停，你企係到等佢地比罰票，罰500,你跑走比再佢地追到，一樣罰500,吾會因為你跑而有額外既罰款的，咁你話比人截停跑定唔跑好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n便衣查飛，好多c9呀叔做，你跑佢地唔會追，（因為佢地心態取易不取難，等下條會ON鳩鳩企係到比佢地罰既傻仔好過。所以你一跑就少左一半危險）<br />\n比較麻煩係後生果班就會追！<br />\n便衣會追因爲佢地係外判，每日都要交數（捉1-2個逃票）！所以會追。<br />\n而黃衫職員多數見你逃票都唔會點處理，更加唔會追你！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係比佢捉到逃票咁點？</span></span><br />\n-罰$500 即場比 （可要求去ATM提款）可以唔出示身分證<br />\n-罰$500 即場比唔到，就要留名留地址（地址真假無人會知，只有你自己知！到時你唔交錢都搵你唔到，真係吹你唔賬）<br />\n-講到明唔會比錢，佢就會控告你，上庭最多罰$5000，但前提係法庭傳票寄到去你個地址先。當你比左真地址收到傳票，上庭前去客務中心交$500罰款都係可以了事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n查飛狗好驚投訴態度同禮貌問題，因為佢地係外判，投訴就一定要問佢<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">名，站名時間。比人投訴就會比In-house 黨鐵問話同要求解釋，有排煩，投訴成唔成立唔係重點！係過程好辛苦</span></span>😭 仲要事前唔同查飛狗講，自己寫信去投訴，咁佢地就備唔到案，In-house 就屌得仲金！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果比查飛狗截停，就忍口唔好講粗口！黨鐵範圍內根據黨鐵附例：爆粗係可以控告上庭罰款。</span></span>最高罰$5000。好撚惡呀黨鐵。<br />\n黨鐵附例以及罰款<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/mtr_by_laws.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Fmtr_by_laws.html&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=35b3e587\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/mtr_by_laws.html</a><br />\n<br />\n『上面都講過，便衣查飛狗每個站最多得2組，你話如果咁多人一齊跳/推桿入閘，佢可以點捉呢。<br />\n就算佢截停到我，後面都仲有幾百個手足等緊幫我做人牆比我跑走呀』<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跳閘救港，唔跳咪用廢老卡囉。<br />\n將慳到嘅錢捐星火同612，買野食比小朋友或者買裝比前線😎</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cda650a956a75ea74001bee0131b7c13f3ef77a0","tid":1543242,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e14a123e40c6431058eb2da660cb51be42f50ea","tid":1543242,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:25:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e92315645d3361ec8284e61b382b12cae5a75b6d","tid":1543242,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb147f48513d6060787952908ba06bc40e5d072","tid":1543242,"uid":81947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>跟我一齊嗌<br />\n驅逐共黨，奪回香港<br />\n全面自治、香港獨立</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2a2d751287aed75c2fed94a22497bfa8bbd18252","tid":1543242,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"各地區連儂牆要人，文宣大量要大人<br />\n解釋清楚！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=f3ed539d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少掂中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.05"},{"pid":"b9831c01fe278ef5a240772624108cd8a7d88fac","tid":1543242,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"咁張揚遲早會提高罰則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb17b7af855acb9d290bccc4c14e828880d35f2","tid":1543242,"uid":207122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:28:00.000Z","msg":"驚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用緊廢老卡"},{"pid":"152c18263f3580246e29625d8c88aca20211f2a0","tid":1543242,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9831c01fe278ef5a240772624108cd8a7d88fac","tid":1543242,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"咁張揚遲早會提高罰則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"罰則唔係問題<br />\n點執法先係問題"},{"pid":"b3632d573e70077ebb0903a192ae998a6eb83273","tid":1543242,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"152c18263f3580246e29625d8c88aca20211f2a0","tid":1543242,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9831c01fe278ef5a240772624108cd8a7d88fac","tid":1543242,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"咁張揚遲早會提高罰則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"罰則唔係問題<br />\n點執法先係問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"只要捉我唔到<br />\n<br />\n罰我一億同罰我一蚊都冇分別"},{"pid":"fb70efd9f376fb4217e8507873b42e0a23bede40","tid":1543242,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">下星期一 9月9 大專罷課集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為大專生<br />\n今次開學罷課搞到咁柒<br />\n完全俾中學生比下去<br />\n知道大家好慚愧 好想付出更多<br />\n<br />\n短時間內嘅主題<br />\n係要美國國會通過香港人權法案<br />\n既然7號有塞機場 8號有美國領事館<br />\n點解我哋大專生<br />\n唔襯中學生9號一週一罷<br />\n一齊搞多次罷課集會<br />\n有聲勢浩大既民意表態<br />\n既可以團聚學界<br />\n又為之後嘅三罷打強心針<br />\n<br />\n7號8號9號 一連三日嘅大型示威集會<br />\n就可以show到民意支持<br />\n俾美國國會順利表決通過條人權法<br />\n<br />\n香港就快死啦<br />\n一齊撐住好唔好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">洗版洗到有組織搞9月9罷課為止</span></span>"},{"pid":"c77adf1ef1f4394b6f2f04fd9aee35e106c168f8","tid":1543242,"uid":261696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"想問港鐵有無權睇/抄身份證"}]}